Finally, note that
\begin{align*}
U^\dag W&=e^{i\pi/4}[cos(\pi/4)-isinn(\pi/4)][cos(\pi/4)+isinn(\pi/4)]\\
&=e^{i\pi/4}cos^2(\pi/4)+ie^{i\pi/4}sinsin(\pi/4)\\
